General.Name: Nupur Recyclers Limited
General.Description: Nupur Recyclers Limited, a metal scrap processing and recycling company, engages in the import, recycling, and trading of non-ferrous metal scrap in India. It imports and recycles metal scrap, such as shredded zinc scrap, zinc die cast scrap, Zurik SS scrap, and aluminium zorba grades. The company was incorporated in 2019 and is based in Delhi, India.
